 We'll call submit_council_vote.\n\nWe need to use mcp with tool aar_submit_council_vote, args JSON string.\n\nLet's do that.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_424d3c15151749b5a2e4442d","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The NOTAMs OIIX A1010/26 and A1015/26 show a broad closure of all airports in the west part of Tehran FIR, a major Iranian airspace region, with only limited daylight exceptions and fresh CAA permission requirements, satisfying the rule's major-closure definition. The closures were initiated by Iran's CAA, were non‑weather‑related, and remained effective past the May 24 2026 11:59 PM ET deadline. Corroborating reports confirm the scope, timing, and security context.\"}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":21331,"output":920,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22251,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781914343252,"responseId":"gen-1781914343-XDQrgxsbgLg53OvyTvWC","responseModel":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b-20230311"}},"message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We have the prompt and the record. We need to decide: vote demonstrated or not_demonstrated. Based on the record, we need to see if Iran initiated a major non-weather closure of its airspace by May 24 2026 11:59 PM ET.\n\nThe plaintiff argues yes, defendant argues no. We need to weigh evidence.\n\nKey evidence: NOTAM OIIX A1010/26 and A1015/26 show \"ALL AIRPORTS IN WEST PART OF TEHRAN FIR ARE CLSD\" except certain airports operational sunrise to sunset, with fresh CAA permission required for civil IFR passenger flights. The NOTAMs are category AD Airport Operations. They do not explicitly mention suspension of commercial flights transiting, arriving in, departing from Iranian airspace or a major